title UTP Match - DFD 04.2 Comparación de carreras con IA

actor "Estudiante\nusuario principal MVP" as Student

package "Proceso de comparación" as Flow #E0F2FE {
  rectangle "P4. Generar comparación\nde carreras" as P4 #DBEAFE
  rectangle "P8. Registrar eventos\ny auditoría" as P8
}

package "Datos requeridos" as DataStores #FFEDD5 {
  database "D1 users\nstudent_profiles\nconsent_records" as D1
  database "D2 vocational_reports" as D2
  database "D3 careers\ncourses\ncareer_courses\nsyllabi" as D3
  database "D4 career_comparisons\nsyllabus_explanations" as D4
  database "D6 event_logs\naudit_logs" as D6
}

package "IA generativa" as External #F5F3FF {
  cloud "E1 Gemini AI\nProveedor IA generativa" as E1
}

Student --> P4 : solicita comparación\nde carreras

P4 --> D1 : lee perfil estudiante
P4 --> D2 : lee scores vocacionales
P4 --> D3 : lee cursos,\nmallas y sílabos

P4 --> E1 : contexto mínimo\n+ prompt
E1 --> P4 : JSON estructurado\nvalidable

P4 --> D4 : guarda comparison_json
P4 --> Student : resumen,\nbarras y narrativa

P4 --> P8 : evento comparación
P8 --> D6 : event_logs\naudit_logs

note right of E1
Regla de IA:
- Enviar solo contexto necesario.
- Evitar datos sensibles innecesarios.
- Validar JSON antes de persistir.
end note

@enduml
```